Thoothi wodaka, thoothi goytika kiam taysate shedayse qaabiysa wocchi dahaa wonin haapaa wombanaasaam kembesana kinka wo yittsade. Kidi yennon goynsa kattsi woylamin kinin qajenna ta yeam kelshadhen goynsa sagi kida wocchimbhe.
Imbaa wontea Yesusin ina imon hayamonka kattsi inin erimennaar ooshimbhattine. Harrna hambhidianna, ogo hayamonin ina imbhoono yeam inin wocchinsoadettsine, yeam inin kaysoadettsitehe.
Ta pir yin yena ida giye: Eedi hayyear malgimi inin dahaadettsi ki qaababhoode; malgimi eedi i maataakaar likka erimeysa dahaadettsi malgimi eedi hayayse iam tiyee.
Inin erimenka malgimi i maatade; ogo inin erimoadettsi iam hayaana yedine. Inta likka eedi i dahaannaar, iam gobsha yeam zaskidine. Harrna hambhidianna, “Kiristoos yisa tarjamonnante kinin yittsaana gembha eenane” yiam hambhaynadara hamin ko dahaakaar tokattine.
Ta ko siyon wodara woam dhacchanna wosa Imba maataa Barjosa bhocchinka Kiristoos wosa seesonna hamayse yiam dembhinna ki imade.
